<p class="reImgeImg"><img src="../../images/Current_B_Img.jpg" width="236" height="149" alt="Investment Account"/></p>
<h1 class="CurrentBN">INVESTMENT ACCOUNT</h1>
<p>Investment Account is an account in which percentage of the deposited funds are invested on the absolute <a title="Mudarabah is a partnership between the Capital Provider and the Entrepreneur, whereby the former receives a share of the profit against his capital and the latter receives a share of the profit against his labor and management. ">Mudaraba</a> basis.</p>
</div>
            <div class="CurrentContent ">
           
            <div class="clr"></div>
            
            

 <h5>Benefits</h5>
<div class="CurrentRight">
<table border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>
<div class="What">
<h3>WHAT DO I NEED?</h3>
<ul>
<li>Account opening form</li>
<li>Copy of national ID or passport copy with a valid residence visa for (for Non UAEians)</li>
<li>Recent utility bill</li>
</ul>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a tabindex="0" href="../../form43ca.html?investmentaccount"><br /><img src="../../images/01.gif" width="284" height="188" alt="Apply Now"/></a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<ul>
<li>Islamic Shari'a Compliant</li>
<li>Competitive semi-annual profit</li>
<li>24/7 ATM access for all ADIB UAE customers</li>
<li>Options to open a joint account</li>
<li>Offered in several currencies</li>
<li>Available through 70 branches all over the country</li>
<li>Debit card issuance; master card electron access to ATM networks and merchant establishments</li>
<li>Issuing Debit Master Card which can be used in ATM networks and Points Of Sale (POS)</li>
</ul>
<h5>Debit Card International Transactions:</h5>
<p>Please be advised that starting May 20th 2016 all international transactions will be disabled on debit cards issued on your EGP Accounts. <br />Should you wish to use your debit card outside UAE, please call our customer service on 10021 to obtain related details.</p>
<h5>Eligibility:</h5>
<ul>
<li>Offered to individuals</li>
<li>Offered to UAEians and foreign residents</li>
</ul>
<h5>Features:</h5>
<ul>
<li>Minimum balance waived from minimum balance fee is EGP 2500 or USD 500 or EURO 500 or STG 500</li>
</ul>
<h5>Profit Calculation:</h5>
<p>Profits and losses are calculated on lowest credit balance during the month, profits or losses are capitalized semi-annually for both local and foreign currency Investment accounts.</p>


           
            
